rvices dynamic secure search remote control network auditing monitoring and alerting software as well as virtual private network services the company also offers software and online services such as security online privacy cloudbased desktop management mobile security management and location services content filtering remote monitoring and other products for various desktop and mobile operating systems its suite of security and it management solutions protect against viruses trojan horses malware suspicious code and other threats and offer a layered approach to threat detection including behavioral monitoring signaturebased threat detection and realtime threat detection with its linkscanner technology the company offers software products in various languages and sells them through the internet and multitiered distribution channels avg technologies nv was founded in  and is based in amsterdam the netherlands avg technologies nv is a subsidiary of avast software bv detailed description gatwickstraat amsterdam   glnetherlandsfounded in  employees phone     wwwavgcom key executives for avg technologies nv avg technologies nv does not have any key executives recorded avg technologies nv key developments avg technologies bv files form  mar   avg technologies bv has announced that it has filed a form  with the securities and exchange commission to voluntarily deregister its ordinary shares nominal value € per share under the securities exchange act of  as amended avg technologies nv will change its ticker to avgtf from avgt nov   effective november   avg technologies nv will change its pink sheets llc stock ticker symbol to avgtf from avgt avg technologies nv announces filing of form  and to be delisted from nyse nov   avast software bv announced the expiration of the subsequent offering period of its previously announced tender offer to purchase all of the outstanding ordinary shares of avg technologies nv for  in cash the subsequent offering period expired at  pm new yor