own request for a youtube video of  pop song never gonna give you up performed by british singer rick astley the video which as of october  has over  million views and  comments had been uploaded in  and was restored within  hours by youtube the videos name refers to the internet meme commonly referred to as rickrolling where someone pranks others by tricking them into going to the video avgs browser addon avg secure search has been criticized as being adware since it is frequently bundled with other software and is often mistakenly installed and exhibits malwarelike behavior avg secure search is also advertised to users of the free versions of avg products although the addon offers legitimate malwareblocking capabilities the default behavior of changing the internet browsers default search engine homepage and new tab page to avg secure search is reminiscent of a potentially unwanted program pup problems uninstalling the addon have been widely reported and the addon could potentially make an internet browser more vulnerable to attacks referencesedit  a b c avg technologies nv financial statements google retrieved  june    avg surpasses  million users worldwide nowavgcom retrieved  march    a b avast acquires antivirus maker avg for bn to gain scale and dive into iot security techcrunch    a b avast closes acquisition of avg technologies september     grisoft celebrates  years of internet security success avg technologies bulletin  december  avgcom  december  retrieved  november    intel buys part of grisoft grisoftcom  september  retrieved  november    intel buys part of avg technologies avgcom  september  retrieved  november    avg technologies announces release of ewido antispyware avgcouk  june  retrieved  november    grisoft announces release of ewido antispyware avgukcom  june  archived from the original on  september  retrieved  november    microsoft incorporates avg into the vista security center avgukcom archived from the original on  september  retrieved  n